dc_title_s: North America: parts of Wisconsin and Michigan sheet V.
dc_description_s: Shows most of Wisconsin and Michigan, parts of Iowa, Illinois, Indiana, and Ohio. Counties and cities are named. Shows railroads, roads, and water features. "Tanner, Smith" in lower left margin. J & C. Walker, sculpt. Sheet 116 from an atlas by the Society for the Diffusion of Useful Knowledge. 1 map: color; 30 x 37 cm This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
dc_creator_sm: Society for the Diffusion of Useful Knowledge (Great Britain)
